    "faq.title": "Questions about Neurowaves",
    "faq.desc": "Straight answers about our IT, marketing, and AI services — process, pricing, and how we work together.",
    "faq.btn": "Didn't find yours?",
    "faq.q1": "What does Neurowaves do?",
    "faq.a1": "We're a full IT, marketing, and AI team for growing businesses. We build websites and web apps, internal and sales systems, CRM and integrations, automate workflows, and embed AI into daily operations — chat and voice bots, generative content, smart analytics. We also run marketing that brings demand: Google Ads, SEO, social, AI creatives, and funnels tied to your stack. One partner connects technology, growth, and operations so leads, data, and teams stay in sync.",
    "faq.q2": "What IT, marketing, and AI services do you cover?",
    "faq.a2": "The full stack your business runs on — not a single plugin. IT: websites, web apps, custom internal and sales systems, CRM, ERP connections, APIs, dashboards, and integrations. Marketing: Google Ads, SEO, content hubs, social automation, AI-generated creatives, and funnels wired to sales. AI: custom chat and voice agents, workflow automation, document Q&A, staff training, and generative tools for your brand. Clients often start with AI Chat Bots, Voice Bot, Google & AI Promotion, or CRM — but we scope every project around your real process, not a fixed menu.",
    "faq.q3": "How does the 2-day audit work?",
    "faq.a3": "In 48 hours we review your website, marketing, forms, chat channels, CRM, team replies, and follow-up habits. You get ten weak spots, ten fixes you can apply immediately, and a roadmap for IT, AI, and marketing automation. It starts from $300 and is the usual first step before a bigger build.",
    "faq.q4": "We don't have a CRM yet — is that a problem?",
    "faq.a4": "No. CRM Implementation is one of our main services — we pick the right platform for your size and process, or build a custom layer on top. Many clients come to us with spreadsheets and chat threads; we turn that into one panel with pipelines, roles, and automation.",
    "faq.q5": "How is your AI chat bot different from a ready-made widget?",
    "faq.a5": "We build bots for your actual job — customer greeting and qualification, internal document Q&A, staff training, analytics — trained on your approved data and wired into your site, messengers, and CRM. Not a generic plugin with a decision tree and your logo on top.",
    "faq.q6": "Do you build AI voice agents for phone calls?",
    "faq.a6": "Yes. Our voice bot handles inbound and outbound calls with natural speech, smart scripts, and logging to your CRM — reminders, confirmations, lead qualification, and routing to the right manager. Projects start from $1,200 depending on call volume and integrations.",
    "faq.q7": "Who is Neurowaves a good fit for?",
    "faq.a7": "B2B companies, service businesses, manufacturing, hospitality, e-commerce, and teams that have outgrown disconnected tools. If inquiries get lost between channels, CRM stages exist only on paper, or marketing and sales don't share one picture — that's where we work.",
    "faq.q8": "How does pricing work?",
    "faq.a8": "Each project is scoped after we understand your process. Public starting points: 2-day audit from $300, AI chat bots from $800, voice bots from $1,200, Google & AI promotion from $1.5k/month, CRM implementation from $2k. Larger custom systems are quoted after analysis.",
    "faq.q9": "Will automation replace our sales team?",
    "faq.a9": "No — we automate the repetitive layer: first replies, sorting, reminders, data entry, standard answers, and scheduled follow-ups. Your people keep judgment calls, negotiations, and closing. The goal is fewer dropped inquiries, not fewer humans.",
    "faq.q10": "How do projects usually start and roll out?",
    "faq.a10": "Most begin with the audit or a focused review call. Then we work in stages: find where time and leads are lost, connect the core (IT stack, site, bots, CRM, marketing, integrations), and only then scale channels that the numbers support. We don't rebuild everything at once unless you ask us to.",
